http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/Order-on-Jayarajan%E2%80%99s-anticipatory-bail-today/article14006276.ece

The District and Sessions Court at Thalassery will pass an order on January 19 on Communist Party of India (Marxist) district secretary P. Jayarajan’s anticipatory bail application in connection with the Central Bureau of Investigation’s (CBI) investigation into the murder of Rashtriya Swayamsevak Sangh (RSS) functionary E. Manoj.The argument of the CBI and the defendant on the anticipatory bail plea was completed in the court on Monday.Mr. Jayarajan moved the anticipatory bail plea on January 11 after the CBI served him a notice to appear before the investigating officers.His plea raised the apprehension that there is ‘politically motivated’ move to arrest and harass him.